^B@2^Z@3^*BKiamemnon: ^*N|cp||at|Of course. Weak Two  Bids are high risk-reward and you have to be very careful when and where to use them. I will give you a list of dos and don'ts for now. Then I can explain more when we look at a few hands. So write down the following critical points:|PG||AT|
